description:
Modern, Art Deco-style luxury hotel near the Arc de Triomphe

In elegant Monceau
This luxuriously appointed hotel places you in the elegant Monceau district, about 700 meters from the Champs-Elysées. You're 2 blocks from Courcelles Metro Station, which will take you to the Louvre in 20 minutes and direct to Montmartre in 15.

Play in the park
Hôtel du Collectionneur Arc de Triomphe is in the middle of the upscale 8th arrondissement, where magnificent Haussmannian buildings grace the streets. You can walk 6 minutes to elegant Parc Monceau for a picnic amid romantic ruins and landscaped gardens.

Relax and unwind
This modern hotel's use of gold and purple hues and Art Deco motifs creates an ambiance that is elegant without being stuffy. You can dine alfresco on the restaurant's 3 terraces, or pamper yourself in the Mosaic Spa with its 10 treatment rooms, steam bath, and fitness center. Free WiFi and 7 meeting rooms also are available.

Art Deco accommodations
Guests report that rooms are spacious, and beautifully decorated in classic Art Deco-inspired style; some have balconies. Amenities include flat-screen TVs, premium bedding, comfortable desks, and coffeemakers. Free WiFi is available in all rooms.

HOTEL_AMENITY.value: Fitness enthusiasts at the Hotel Du Collectionneur Arc de Triomphe Paris can work up a sweat on the cardio and weight machines in the hotel gym, and for those who need extra encouragement, a personal trainer is available on request. After a workout, guests can unwind in the Mosaic Spa, which offers a steam room, sauna, a hydrotonic bath with massaging jet showers and a range of indulgent massage and beauty treatments. The hotel can arrange sightseeing excursions around the city and surrounding area, including private VIP tours in a number of languages. Multilingual staff at the 24-hour front desk can arrange babysitting and dry-cleaning services, exchange currency and provide round-the-clock room service. Guests arriving by car will find secure, covered parking facilities on site, with valet parking services provided on request (surcharges apply). Free WiFi and 7 meeting rooms also are available.

DINING.value:
Le Safran - International restaurant housed in a large dining room with picture windows and three terraces. Open for breakfast, lunch and dinner, and brunch on Sundays.
Purple Bar - Casual Art Deco bar with gilded fluting, intimate alcoves, tasselled chandeliers, wrought iron and fine woodwork, serving coffee and croissants in the morning, snacks all day and cocktails in the evening.
Please check the Rooms and Rates page to see which rates include breakfast.

RECREATION.value: The recreational activities listed below are available either on site or near the hotel; fees may apply.

Special requests are subject to availability upon check-in and may incur additional charges. Special requests cannot be guaranteed.

LOCATION_TEASER.value:
By Parc de Monceau
A modern seven-storey Paris hotel inspired by the Art Deco style, overlooking Parc de Monceau, one kilometre from the Champs-Élysées.

During renovations, the hotel will make every effort to minimize noise and disturbance.

GOLD.value: Set in the upscale 8th arrondissement, less than 1 km from the Arc de Triomphe and Champs-Elysées, this large, elegant hotel combines modern facilities with the romance of Art Deco styling. Amenities including a full-service spa, free WiFi, a restaurant with outdoor dining terraces, and a fashionable bar bring a luxury touch. Guests rave about friendly staff.
